props.name: columnKey
props.description: Identifier of a column if field property is not defined.

props.name: field
props.description: Property represented by the column.

props.name: sortField
props.description: Property name to use in sorting, defaults to field.

props.name: filterField
props.description: Property name to use in filtering, defaults to field.

props.name: dataType
props.description: Type of data. It's value is related to PrimeVue.filterMatchModeOptions config.

props.name: sortable
props.description: Defines if a column is sortable.

props.name: header
props.description: Header content of the column.

props.name: footer
props.description: Footer content of the column.

props.name: style
props.description: Inline style of header, body and footer cells.

props.name: class
props.description: Style class of header, body and footer cells.

props.name: headerStyle
props.description: Inline style of the column header.

props.name: headerClass
props.description: Style class of the column header.

props.name: bodyStyle
props.description: Inline style of the column body.

props.name: bodyClass
props.description: Style class of the column body.

props.name: footerStyle
props.description: Inline style of the column footer.

props.name: footerClass
props.description: Style class of the column footer.

props.name: showFilterMenu
props.description: Whether to display the filter overlay.

props.name: showFilterOperator
props.description: When enabled, match all and match any operator selector is displayed.

props.name: showClearButton
props.description: Displays a button to clear the column filtering.

props.name: showApplyButton
props.description: Displays a button to apply the column filtering.

props.name: showFilterMatchModes
props.description: Whether to show the match modes selector.

props.name: showAddButton
props.description: When enabled, a button is displayed to add more rules.

props.name: filterMatchModeOptions
props.description: An array of label-value pairs to override the global match mode options.

props.name: maxConstraints
props.description: Maximum number of constraints for a column filter.

props.name: excludeGlobalFilter
props.description: Whether to exclude from global filtering or not.

props.name: filterHeaderStyle
props.description: Inline style of the column filter header in row filter display.

props.name: filterHeaderClass
props.description: Style class of the column filter header in row filter display.

props.name: filterMenuStyle
props.description: Inline style of the column filter overlay.

props.name: filterMenuClass
props.description: Style class of the column filter overlay.

props.name: selectionMode
props.description: Defines column based selection mode.

props.name: expander
props.description: Displays an icon to toggle row expansion.

props.name: colspan
props.description: Number of columns to span for grouping.

props.name: rowspan
props.description: Number of rows to span for grouping.

props.name: rowReorder
props.description: Whether this column displays an icon to reorder the rows.

props.name: rowReorderIcon
props.description: Icon of the drag handle to reorder rows.

props.name: reorderableColumn
props.description: Defines if the column itself can be reordered with dragging.

props.name: rowEditor
props.description: When enabled, column displays row editor controls.

props.name: frozen
props.description: Whether the column is fixed in horizontal scrolling.

props.name: alignFrozen
props.description: Position of a frozen column, valid values are left and right.

props.name: exportable
props.description: Whether the column is included in data export.

props.name: exportHeader
props.description: Custom export header of the column to be exported as CSV.

props.name: exportFooter
props.description: Custom export footer of the column to be exported as CSV.

props.name: filterMatchMode
props.description: Defines the filtering algorithm to use when searching the options.

props.name: hidden
props.description: Whether the column is rendered.

props.name: dt
props.description: It generates scoped CSS variables using design tokens for the component.

props.name: pt
props.description: Used to pass attributes to DOM elements inside the component.

props.name: ptOptions
props.description: Used to configure passthrough(pt) options of the component.

props.name: unstyled
props.description: When enabled, it removes component related styles in the core.
